result.name: 美味佳

reviews.text: The food might be cheap, but it's too oily and everything tastes very salty. It's not the kind of food you should eat regularly if you want to be healthy. Also, the wait time is unreasonably long and they need to do a much better job with the hygiene.

Firstly, it is importance to bring along with your smartphone when visiting the restaurant and must spare more times for waiting, as it takes about 30 to 45 minutes between placing order and dishes on the table.
The grill foods are tasted strong and a bite salty, foods are almost having the same taste but with difference texture according to the foods, as they use the same seasoning powder.
It is recommended to the restaurant to have one-off order, as additional order takes times (30 to 45 minutes), this would lowering the turnover of the “tables” and overall turnover eventually. (Simulating the Hunger marketing strategy)
Will try their "cart noodle" next time.

Great local bbq store with second branch nearby. Lot of different choices, meat, beans, veggie, bean curd, mushroom, intestine, seafood etc. spicy or not, salted or less oil, you just voice out to make it happen. Sometimes you may need to queue if having it there. Or you may wait for a while for take away.
Cheap and tasty :)
Quite tasty but too oily

reviews.text: 味道OK越多學生肥冰加油我是小雨點
啲肉臭㗎，老闆仲去參加暴動，死暴徒嚟
間店糸支持送中人士！ 罷食
其實我自己覺得D食物好壞參半la, 有部份係幾出色嘅, E.g. 雞奕、金菇、雞批菇、茄子, 但有部份吾係太咸就真頭係好難食, E.g. 牛肉九菜, 真係要吐返出來，所以我覺得吾值得排咁耐隊入去，同埋就算入到去坐低都等好耐先有食物上，最後我地一行12人坐左兩小時都仲未上晒D野，未燒ge cut單走人

The food might be cheap, but it's too oily and everything tastes very salty. It's not the kind of food you should eat regularly if you want to be healthy. Also, the wait time is unreasonably long and they need to do a much better job with the hygiene.
